blicGreeter.class);\n        assertThat(method.getName()).isEqualTo(\"greet\");\n    }\n\n    public interface PublicGreeter {\n        String greet();\n    }\n\n    private static class HiddenGreeter implements PublicGreeter {\n        @Override\n        public String greet() {\n            return \"hello\";\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1780732732748}}
